00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:11.390 align:middle line:84%
so let me ask you
guys some questions.

00:01:11.390 --> 00:01:17.060 align:middle line:84%
Last time was our first applied
lecture on risk sharing.

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:21.740 align:middle line:84%
We did it in both village
India and medieval villages.

00:01:21.740 --> 00:01:24.710 align:middle line:84%
And today, I want to give
a little bit more emphasis

00:01:24.710 --> 00:01:29.000 align:middle line:84%
